News.Title: Frog Cellsat Secures Major Contract for Navi Mumbai International Airport
News.Summary: Frog Cellsat has won its third significant OneDAS contract in the past three months. This latest contract, valued at over INR 16 crore, is for the Navi Mumbai International Airport project.

News.Title: Frog Cellsat Secures Major Contract for Navi Mumbai International Airport
News.Summary: Frog Cellsat has won its third significant ONEDAS (One Network for Emergency and Daily Activities System) contract in the past three months. This latest contract, valued at over 16 crore Indian Rupees, is for the Navi Mumbai International Airport project. The company's success in securing multiple large contracts in a short period indicates strong growth and market demand for their services in the infrastructure and communication sectors.
